						data-src="https://file1.science-et-vie.com/var/scienceetvie/storage/images/media/anciennes-images/s-amp-v-1175-paranormal/27523-1-fre-FR/S-amp-V-1175-paranormal.jpg?alias=square500x500&size=x100&format=jpeg" class="lazy" alt="S&amp;amp;amp;V 1175 - paranormal" data-title="S&amp;amp;amp;V 1175 - paranormal" height="500" width="500"></picture></a></li><li><a  href="https://www.science-et-vie.com/science-et-culture/x-files-coma-bioterrorisme-epidemies-la-10e-serie-se-clot-aux-frontieres-de-la-biologie-6621/(page)/5" class="responsive-img image "><picture  data-uri="nUE0pUZ6Yl93q3php2AcMJ5wMF1yqP12nJHhL29gY3AwnJIhL2HgMKDgL3IfqUIlMF94YJMcoTImYJAioJRgLzyiqTIlpz9lnKAgMF1ypTyxMJ1cMKZgoTRgZGOyYKAypzyyYKAyYJAfo3DgLKI4YJMlo250nJIlMKZgMTHgoTRgLzyioT9anJHgAwLlZF8bpTSaMFxiAD==" onclick="goToSculturL(event);" onmousedown="goToSculturL(event);" class="sculturL responsive-img lazy"><source media="(min-width: 1190px)" srcset="" data-src="https://file1.science-et-vie.com/var/scienceetvie/storage/images/media/anciennes-images/s-amp-v-1011-bioterrorisme/27715-1-fre-FR/S-amp-V-1011-bioterrorisme.jpg?alias=square500x500&size=x100&format=webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(min-width: 791px)" srcset="" data-src="https://file1.science-et-vie.com/var/scienceetvie/storage/images/media/anciennes-images/s-amp-v-1011-bioterrorisme/27715-1-fre-FR/S-amp-V-1011-bioterrorisme.jpg?alias=square500x500&size=x75&format=webp" type="image/webp"><source   srcset="" data-src="https://file1.science-et-vie.com/var/scienceetvie/storage/images/media/anciennes-images/s-amp-v-1011-bioterrorisme/27715-1-fre-FR/S-amp-V-1011-bioterrorisme.jpg?alias=square500x500&size=x50&format=webp" type="image/webp"><img
